text: Where Wight Kings were powerful warriors & heroes ressurected Dusk Wight are powerful sorcerers & scholars.
Many of dragon sibilings are missing or lost, the scions of those lost have grown disillusioned in the Empire of the Celestial Dragon and now tread a darker paths for power.
Once a scion from a Dynasty in the Nonchang basin, he traveled to distant Lahmia and returned a powerful Necromancer at the whim of a lord he called Harakhte.
The keeper of the arcane lore casts terrible curses, summoning vengeful desert spirits to feast upon their souls.
Necromancers are amongst the most cursed of all those who practice the magical arts, for they have exchanged their humanity for the ability to raise the dead.
A single Banshee is a terrifying prospect, and even those warriors skilled enough to match blades with a Vampire have little defence against her unnatural screams.
